725671f.title: Queens: 82nd Street - Roosevelt Avenue
725671f.text:
82nd Street, at the N.W. corner of Roosevelt Avenue,
showing the new Corn Exchange Bank and adjoining commercial
buildings. Note the stairway to the subway elevated station.
Brown Brothers  About 1928
NO REPRODUCTIONS

725670f-a.title: Queens: 82nd Street - Roosevelt Avenue
725670f-a.text:
82nd Street (left), at the N.E. corner of Roosevelt
Avenue, showing the Whelan Drug store occupying the corner
site. On Roosevelt Avenue is the elevated station of the
I.R.T.-B.1.T. subway.
Brown Brothers  About 1928
NO REPRODUCTIONS
